Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,period and the body is is an it that walks around and if you hit that level
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find that everybody talks to the body as though it's you which is very
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,mystical in the beginning you can't what you wonder who they're talking to who in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the world are they talking to and you realize that they all think you're the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,body and once you get that you're you're okay you get used to people talking to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it because they think it's you anyway so those are the levels of enlightenment a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from 600 up are formerly sat chitinanda heavenly bliss and peace all time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,stops and at that level you can leave the body if you wish at level 600 you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer consider yourself to be in that body and if you wish to leave you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,may you realize this there's an open invitation and karma plays a big point
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in part there and whether you're going to stay with the body or not but you go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,into a state of bliss and whether you live or not is irrelevant so those are
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels from the lowest of hatred and hatefulness and imagine people people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,live in this level they're constantly angry they hate the world they hate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,everything so how you see the world today we're going to talk about what is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,how you see the world depends on where you are on this level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see it as a hateful place as an evil place hopeless sad and tragic scary
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and frightening disappointing conflictual see the world is demanding
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can see the world as satisfactory hopeful you realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,harmony is possible you can see that the world is peaceful you can see that the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,meaningful you begin to see the world is benign complete beautiful and perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and very often the revelation so that shifting from ordinary consciousness into
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a very high state of consciousness is a revelation I've described the occurrences
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in my own life and the way the world is perceived so we'll be talking a lot today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about how the world is perceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a couple of experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One is the room lighting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Wilson, the founder of AA, describes it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an atheist for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then realized that unless he believed in God,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he was certain to die of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was an atheist,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and so he didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So he struggled and he struggled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And one day he just gave up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the room lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The room lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With an illumination of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was a profound, transformative experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At another time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in the world becomes extremely beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because the divinity of all that exists reveals itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and divinity is perfect and incredibly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind explaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let her describe these two events in her life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've described them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've described mine so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.95,0:22:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the light in the room is like Bill Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And so one time, you tell him about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and then tell him about when you're driving around the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's how the world's perfection comes about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So they think it's not just a peculiarity of me personally, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's weird, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, now it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a very high experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it usually, many times people say that it comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,just before you awaken, you know, about four in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're just at that time when you're almost going to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or almost waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when a lot of the higher experiences seem to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And then afterwards you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,am I going crazy or did this really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But in my particular experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this illuminating light that came from the corner of the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the corner of the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was laying there and my eyes were wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wide awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden this light came into the room and it was blinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't see any object in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all engulfing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was like a peaceful energy that came with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And almost,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,awe-striking energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it came into the room and lit up the whole room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't see an object in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.68,0:24:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing was available sense-wise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.22,0:24:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,except for this energy that was so loving and so earth-moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.60,0:24:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Wilson, who I knew personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.06,0:24:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,described it exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.42,0:24:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you had that experience and described it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.78,0:24:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it was almost like Bill was talking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.40,0:24:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.68,0:24:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the light was coming from the corners of the room and blinding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.66,0:24:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was coming from one corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.12,0:24:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole light just came in from one corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.94,0:24:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was like, it wasn't the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.56,0:24:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.06,0:24:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.98,0:24:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called illumination.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.42,0:25:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it went into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.50,0:25:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The light just kind of funneled into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.92,0:25:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that is when we started teaching the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.14,0:25:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was almost like the guiding light, if you want to put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.38,0:25:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.76,0:25:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It changed my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.94,0:25:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Several months after that, we live up in Sedona, as you all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.94,0:25:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was driving down Upper Red Rock Loop Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.78,0:25:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden, this earth-changing phenomena took place
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.40,0:25:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,where you could see every single leaf on every tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Every rock seemed to be three-dimensional.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.18,0:25:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're standing, as I'm driving down,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.60,0:25:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I literally had to pull off the side of the road
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.60,0:25:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and sit there for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.22,0:25:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you got the whole impression that the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and all your surroundings were a part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.81,0:25:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.97,0:26:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very moving experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.94,0:26:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's hard to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.49,0:26:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.58,0:26:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are the things we're going to be talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.17,0:26:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.67,0:26:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place where you can become illuminated,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.43,0:26:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and become enlightened, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.09,0:26:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a world of great light.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.53,0:26:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world of great spiritual opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.53,0:26:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's a place of maximum spiritual opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.53,0:26:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.53,0:26:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.59,0:26:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just thought we'd cover the basics,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.59,0:26:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll go on to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.59,0:26:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.59,0:26:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to go through the review slides rather quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.07,0:26:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.49,0:26:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go through the review slides rather quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.52,0:26:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the enlightened states.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.32,0:27:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the states of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.45,0:27:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.45,0:27:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the experiences which you can calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.25,0:27:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way up to a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.25,0:27:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are the states of enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.12,0:27:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and it goes all the way up to the archangels,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.12,0:27:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and then all the way to divinity itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.63,0:27:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,which is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.63,0:27:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I came out of the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.46,0:27:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of eternal agony in the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.94,0:27:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,which I had fallen into through exploring the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.62,0:27:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and I began exploring the depths of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.62,0:27:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went into the levels of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.90,0:27:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and first it was the higher hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.26,0:28:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,people just in agony and having their heads cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.26,0:28:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I went into the depths of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.54,0:28:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, the depths of hell are beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.12,0:28:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I suggest to everybody that they avoid hell at all cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal, hell is eternal agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.66,0:28:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the heavenly states are eternal bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.66,0:28:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the lower levels of hell were eternal agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.91,0:28:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember passing a sign that said,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.36,0:28:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon all hope, ye who enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.74,0:28:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Dante says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.74,0:28:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And how Dante knew it, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.74,0:28:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.74,0:28:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you see suffering and agony
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.00,0:28:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the hopelessness and despair that is forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.45,0:28:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you go deeper into the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize what forever means.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.25,0:29:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The horribleness of forever cut off from the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.89,0:29:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever agonizing despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.89,0:29:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I advise people not to play with hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.40,0:29:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,People play with hell, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.91,0:29:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's like a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.91,0:29:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.04,0:29:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.71,0:29:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the pits of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.71,0:29:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pits of hell where I was in eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.03,0:29:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you can only experience eternity in the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.03,0:29:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in the pits of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.67,0:29:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So it went on for an eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.67,0:29:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was an atheist at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.22,0:29:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.38,0:29:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a God, I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.38,0:29:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I went blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.73,0:29:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when I came to,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.73,0:30:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the world had been transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.02,0:30:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,into the most incredible, radiant beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.08,0:30:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The light shone forth from the existence and divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.75,0:30:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,all that exists, the divinity of all that exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.75,0:30:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,shone forth in exquisite splendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the major transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.98,0:30:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.98,0:30:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.65,0:30:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why we got to talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.65,0:30:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, because of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.65,0:30:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of this slide, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.65,0:30:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so what's the next slide, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.81,0:30:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.13,0:30:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we said that most of the world's population
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.13,0:30:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,lives below the level of 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.13,0:30:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, 85% of the world lives below
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.13,0:30:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what to us would be like the upper levels of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.13,0:30:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,despair and poverty and crime and agony and hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.13,0:30:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's where 85% of the world's population lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.61,0:31:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, they live below level 200, 85% of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.64,0:31:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, the average level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.41,0:31:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world right now is, what did we say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.41,0:31:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,204, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.46,0:31:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.46,0:31:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the few people, these are the few people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.46,0:31:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who calibrate 250 and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.04,0:31:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You see how few they are compared to the mass
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.04,0:31:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of people in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.23,0:31:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The great majority of people in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.23,0:31:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,live below level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.23,0:31:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.26,0:31:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll turn, go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.26,0:31:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be because the 15% who calibrate over 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.58,0:31:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,their relative power is so much greater
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.44,0:31:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,than the negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.44,0:31:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.98,0:32:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The 15% of the world calibrate, 15% calibrate above 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.56,0:32:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Counterbalance is the 85% that calibrate below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.56,0:32:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.32,0:32:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So a group like this has a profound and significant impact
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.32,0:32:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,on the consciousness of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.32,0:32:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound grandiose?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.98,0:32:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.44,0:32:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.55,0:32:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you sitting here in this audience right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.55,0:32:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,here present, are way over here and you're counterbalancing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a huge mass of the population.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.74,0:32:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So this audience here present now
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.74,0:32:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is counterbalancing literally millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.74,0:32:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.98,0:32:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here now is calibrating,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.98,0:33:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is counterbalancing the negativity literally of millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.98,0:33:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were not so,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.02,0:33:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,then humanity would just self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.02,0:33:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It would self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.02,0:33:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So because of this 15%,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.02,0:33:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the 85% does not destroy itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.02,0:33:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.08,0:33:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The evolution of consciousness over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.98,0:33:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the scale of the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.98,0:33:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the animals starting way out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.98,0:33:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from the bacteria, protozoa,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.98,0:33:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,coming up through the fish, the octopus,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.98,0:33:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the Komodo dragon, the dinosaur,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.98,0:33:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the whale, migratory birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.36,0:33:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get to the wild animals
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.49,0:33:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and the wolf, the hippopotamus.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.49,0:33:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get to the domestic pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.49,0:33:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.49,0:33:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally get up to the piggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.49,0:33:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, these are all killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.52,0:33:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to eat and live, they have to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get to the peaceful animals
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.52,0:34:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that are herbivorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.52,0:34:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A deer doesn't have to kill anybody to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.52,0:34:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The elk don't have to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.55,0:34:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lower levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.55,0:34:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,live by the death of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.62,0:34:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So they are destructive to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.95,0:34:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so the only reason they stay alive
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.95,0:34:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is by killing you, a tiger or the lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.95,0:34:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't blame them for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.40,0:34:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't want to play with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.88,0:34:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we move up the scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.20,0:34:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see, you come to the domestic animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.20,0:34:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you come to the family dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.20,0:34:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and the gorilla, and Oscar the cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.62,0:34:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex, the trained African gray parrot who talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.94,0:34:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Alex, you see, calibrates over 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.94,0:34:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Alex actually understands
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.94,0:35:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.16,0:35:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say to Alex, get me two blue cubes,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.16,0:35:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex understands two blue cubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So Alex is a very famous parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.44,0:35:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And Coco, the trained gorilla, calibrates at 405.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.73,0:35:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are safer with Coco, the trained gorilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.95,0:35:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,than you are with 85% of the people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.50,0:35:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, and here's where I go soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.72,0:35:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitty's purr is 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.72,0:35:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and a dog's wagging tail is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.23,0:35:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've got three kitties home
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.33,0:35:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and a doggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.33,0:35:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So this morning, all the kitties,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.33,0:35:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,all three of them were around me purring away,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.33,0:35:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,giving me something to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.33,0:35:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the doggie's tail was wagging like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.39,0:35:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, now you have to stay home and guard the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.39,0:36:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So they have become man's companions,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.71,0:36:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,man's companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.43,0:36:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, we have, oh, I'm sorry about,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.43,0:36:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we have Broccoli, who is a talking parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.46,0:36:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And Broccoli carries on a conversation all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.46,0:36:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Never stops talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.49,0:36:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And she calls to the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.58,0:36:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And she calls the kitties.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.58,0:36:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, kitty, kitty, kitty, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.13,0:36:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the dog's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.25,0:36:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'll say, Kelsey, Kelsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.25,0:36:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the dog runs over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.25,0:36:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.30,0:36:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon as I was telling the dog, get away from the bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.30,0:36:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So then Kelsey will say, and then the bird will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.30,0:36:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,get away from that bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.30,0:36:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.30,0:36:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And what else did you, oh, she taught the bird to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.08,0:36:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,shop till you drop, put it on the credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.84,0:37:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shop till you drop, put it on the credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.42,0:37:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.42,0:37:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.42,0:37:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise we'll never get through to the new material.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.42,0:37:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.42,0:37:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.64,0:37:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.64,0:37:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.64,0:37:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the level of the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.64,0:37:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the intellectual capital of civilization,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.64,0:37:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the great books of the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.64,0:37:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,which all calibrate in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.64,0:37:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the intellect of the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.74,0:37:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great scientists, Darwin, Copernicus,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.89,0:37:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great philosophers, Hegel, Hobbes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.11,0:37:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Immanuel Kant, Locke,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.38,0:37:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the structure of Western civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.96,0:38:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what the Pope is worried is under threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.41,0:38:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's afraid that the Western society is going to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.41,0:38:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And he points to Europe and says that these level of the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.41,0:38:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,are collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.60,0:38:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are collapsing and calibrating lower and lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.60,0:38:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So Europe no longer calibrates as high as it once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.60,0:38:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And the impact then of the great books of the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.95,0:38:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what has been substituted is social Marxism.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's being taught in a lot of colleges today
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.94,0:38:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the great books of the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.94,0:38:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrated in the 400s, but cultural Marxism.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.94,0:38:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you see, Karl Marx calibrates at 130.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.94,0:38:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're going to substitute 130
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.65,0:38:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for 455, Adam Smith,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.65,0:39:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the wealth of nations is the basis of capitalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.65,0:39:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to replace what calibrates at 455
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.29,0:39:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with collectivism, which calibrates at 130.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.29,0:39:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And collectivism, where it has been tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.29,0:39:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,has caused collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.29,0:39:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In China, 10 million people starved to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.29,0:39:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million starved to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.29,0:39:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Substituting this for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.48,0:39:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So the calibrated levels of consciousness, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.48,0:39:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,are profoundly important.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.58,0:39:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the first thing I want to know about somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.58,0:39:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or a speaker, somebody on television,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.64,0:39:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is what does this person calibrate at?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.64,0:39:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Having calibrated thousands of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.67,0:39:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you eventually get pretty good at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.67,0:39:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can guess, you know, almost within 10 degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.67,0:39:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of what level this person is speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.74,0:39:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you want to know is how much truth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.74,0:39:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is there to what they are saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.74,0:40:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.38,0:40:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll skip this one. It's too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.41,0:40:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll skip this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.88,0:40:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll skip this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.84,0:40:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sort of an explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.84,0:40:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of why this muscle test works.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.84,0:40:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't understand it based on Newtonian physics,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.84,0:40:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which is based on cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.84,0:40:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quantum effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.35,0:40:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So the understanding of the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.35,0:40:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that I demonstrate here with Susan all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.35,0:40:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with, the understanding is quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.54,0:40:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only, the best, nearest understanding to it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.58,0:40:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,would be reading the new book, Mindful Universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.58,0:40:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,by the professor of physics at Berkeley,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.58,0:40:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,whose name I always forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.09,0:40:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What was his name? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.47,0:40:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Henry Stepp, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.47,0:41:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're really interested in understanding it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.47,0:41:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, here he is right here. I knew he was someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.30,0:41:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Henry Stepp, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.30,0:41:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the, what happens is you collapse the wave function
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.30,0:41:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,from potential to actual.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.43,0:41:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're witnessing all the time is emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.43,0:41:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not witnessing causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.53,0:41:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.53,0:41:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind thinks in Newtonian terms of cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.94,0:41:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening is the potentiality becomes an actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.94,0:41:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,by an ascent of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.94,0:41:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.24,0:41:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.00,0:41:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You folks did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.00,0:41:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality becomes an actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.18,0:42:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,by an ascent of the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.42,0:42:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are not caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.42,0:42:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality emerges.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.42,0:42:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens is this situation here has a potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.58,0:42:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the influence of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.58,0:42:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that potentiality becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.98,0:42:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the influence of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.55,0:42:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what could be does become what it could be
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.62,0:42:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if local conditions are favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.80,0:42:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put water on it, it'll grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.80,0:42:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't put water on it, it won't grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.80,0:42:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mind thinks in Newtonian terms of cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.27,0:42:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's a quantum reality
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.27,0:42:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in which potentiality actualizes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.27,0:42:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,due to an ascent of the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.27,0:42:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The potentiality becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.75,0:43:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, but that did it by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.98,0:43:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego jumps in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.98,0:43:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego jumps in and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.98,0:43:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to put my arm out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.23,0:43:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.59,0:43:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.59,0:43:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It decided to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.07,0:43:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the it that decided it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.58,0:43:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't time to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.86,0:43:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Run through your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.86,0:43:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll put my arm out to demonstrate a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.86,0:43:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't time to think it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.63,0:43:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No thinking went on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.02,0:43:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.14,0:43:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No thinking went on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.49,0:43:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No thinking went on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.55,0:44:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You folks probably think
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.75,0:44:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that everything you do is because you think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.84,0:44:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fess up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.83,0:44:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is that aspect of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.78,0:44:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.88,0:44:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it presumes, it presumes that it is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.88,0:44:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It presumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.88,0:44:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you're not the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.35,0:44:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the witness of these phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.35,0:44:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena are spontaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.99,0:44:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The phenomena of life are happening of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.99,0:44:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality becoming an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.47,0:44:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, frankly, of the radiance of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.50,0:44:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the radiance of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.76,0:44:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,all potentiality can become an actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.76,0:45:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,when the local conditions are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.05,0:45:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because of your consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.05,0:45:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but because of the presence of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.05,0:45:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.08,0:45:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is what allows all potentiality to become an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.08,0:45:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.37,0:45:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.37,0:45:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.85,0:45:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it simple, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.42,0:45:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These are spiritual practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.42,0:45:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.58,0:45:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're in one of the books, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.64,0:45:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives you the calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.64,0:45:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of various spiritual techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.02,0:45:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Practicing the golden rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.02,0:45:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Turning fair wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.02,0:45:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See, they all calibrate around 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.02,0:45:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.02,0:45:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to communion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.12,0:45:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All these things calibrate around 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.12,0:45:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gregorian chants.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.12,0:46:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Om Namah Shivaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.12,0:46:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Genuflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.31,0:46:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kneeling to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.31,0:46:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Clasping your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.31,0:46:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All devotional acts are 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.24,0:46:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you experience a culture
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.24,0:46:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,where everyone greets the other person thusly,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.24,0:46:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you're in a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.30,0:46:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.30,0:46:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,than Broadway in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.30,0:46:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A world in which everyone greets everyone else this way
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.82,0:46:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,acknowledges divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.01,0:46:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I acknowledge divinity within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.10,0:46:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.10,0:46:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.78,0:46:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.78,0:46:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.19,0:46:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to do with brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.22,0:46:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, below level 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.32,0:46:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,above and below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.86,0:47:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you have different brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.90,0:47:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain function above 200
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is different than the brain function below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.09,0:47:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.09,0:47:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't people do this, that, and the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.15,0:47:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because they're operating
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.31,0:47:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,from a different side of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.66,0:47:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So the animal side of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.66,0:47:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is interested in conquering,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.66,0:47:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and acquisition,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.66,0:47:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.66,0:47:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the spiritual side of the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.66,0:47:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,works in a whole different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.66,0:47:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.66,0:47:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you have right brain dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.66,0:47:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.56,0:47:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as you become involved in spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.56,0:47:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or any spiritual practice
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.82,0:47:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or any spiritual congregation
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.82,0:47:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or attending a lecture like this
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.82,0:47:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.94,0:47:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you summon forth
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.94,0:47:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what's classically been called
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.94,0:47:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the kundalini energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.94,0:47:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.97,0:48:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which classically is described
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.97,0:48:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as going about the spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.51,0:48:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The kundalini energy then rises
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.54,0:48:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to the various chakras,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.54,0:48:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to the various chakras
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.54,0:48:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or energy centers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.54,0:48:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And they get higher and higher
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.70,0:48:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,until finally they reach
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.70,0:48:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the crown chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.89,0:48:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.89,0:48:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so by being as loving as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.89,0:48:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.89,0:48:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.89,0:48:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you're summoning forth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.89,0:48:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.89,0:48:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to radiate up to the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.89,0:48:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you get up to the brow.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.05,0:48:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to develop spiritual vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.05,0:48:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally to the crown chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.05,0:48:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.05,0:48:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's actually
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.34,0:48:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a physiologic change in the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.34,0:48:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurs as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.34,0:48:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of becoming spiritually oriented,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.34,0:48:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually committed,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.34,0:48:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,joining spiritual groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.34,0:48:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Practicing spiritual principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.62,0:49:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just simply praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.91,0:49:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Genuflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.91,0:49:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All things that are symbolic
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.46,0:49:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of acknowledgement
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.46,0:49:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.46,0:49:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.46,0:49:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin to transform you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.81,0:49:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.81,0:49:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and see the world differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.81,0:49:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So when we say,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.87,0:49:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.87,0:49:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.87,0:49:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the world is?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.87,0:49:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the world is?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.87,0:49:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It pretty much depends considerably
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.87,0:49:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,on where your Kundalini energy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.87,0:49:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is risen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.87,0:49:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A person is risen to the third eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.94,0:49:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,sees the world differently
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.94,0:49:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,than a person who is holding
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.94,0:49:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,their energy in the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.94,0:49:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding it in the spleen,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.77,0:49:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you see an enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.77,0:49:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a world of attack and revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.77,0:49:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,attack and revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.77,0:49:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,attack and revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.31,0:49:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There are whole cultures
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.79,0:49:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,on the planet today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.79,0:49:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that have a dominant effect
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.79,0:50:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,on human history right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.24,0:50:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole culture lives in the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.30,0:50:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.30,0:50:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.30,0:50:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the population,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.30,0:50:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.30,0:50:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,lives in the spleen chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.66,0:50:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.39,0:50:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.42,0:50:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.42,0:50:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,get even,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.42,0:50:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,dominate,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.42,0:50:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.42,0:50:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,behead,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.42,0:50:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,chop their heads off, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.99,0:50:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To people who live in the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.99,0:50:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,this seems mysterious and unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.25,0:50:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.25,0:50:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,they often go into denial
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.25,0:50:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.25,0:50:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, people can't really be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.25,0:50:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, guess they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.82,0:50:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.82,0:50:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Little mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.82,0:50:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.27,0:50:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.27,0:50:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and social problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.27,0:50:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I show this because
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.38,0:50:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this phenomenon is politicized.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.38,0:50:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In politicizing things,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.82,0:51:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a condition is blamed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.82,0:51:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on other people
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.82,0:51:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,or our circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.82,0:51:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.82,0:51:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.27,0:51:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,when we look at level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.27,0:51:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rate of unemployment,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.27,0:51:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.27,0:51:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of unemployment
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.50,0:51:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is not related to available jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.50,0:51:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's related to level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.50,0:51:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At this consciousness level here,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.17,0:51:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,75% of the people are unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.16,0:51:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.16,0:51:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with how many jobs there are available.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.16,0:51:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to do with that whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.42,0:51:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of unemployment,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.64,0:51:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.64,0:51:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.64,0:51:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.64,0:51:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.50,0:51:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the rate of criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.63,0:51:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can blame them
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.63,0:51:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,on external factors,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.63,0:51:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but you see that they are all
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.63,0:51:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,completely related
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.63,0:51:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.63,0:51:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What to this person
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.86,0:51:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is something we can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.86,0:51:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go out and beat up people,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.86,0:51:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,would not even be thinkable
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.86,0:51:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.14,0:52:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So social problems
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.18,0:52:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,reflect completely and 100%
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.18,0:52:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.34,0:52:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.34,0:52:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.05,0:52:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.05,0:52:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here on the right-hand side,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.05,0:52:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we see the rate of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.05,0:52:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,At the lower levels,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.05,0:52:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,30% are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.14,0:52:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we see,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.69,0:52:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.69,0:52:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,percent is 4%,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.91,0:52:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.91,0:52:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all below 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.91,0:52:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,People who live in fear, 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.91,0:52:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry, 12%.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.91,0:52:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride, a lot of people live in pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.91,0:52:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,22%.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.10,0:52:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you see
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.10,0:52:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at the higher the level
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.10,0:52:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.10,0:52:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the percent of people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.10,0:52:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,who are happy
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.10,0:52:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,goes up immensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.10,0:52:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So spiritually oriented,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.10,0:52:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.10,0:52:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually oriented people,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.10,0:53:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,500 and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.10,0:53:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the chances are probably 90%
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.10,0:53:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're relatively happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.10,0:53:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so used to being happy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.00,0:53:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you're not happy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.00,0:53:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for a moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.00,0:53:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you're unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.51,0:53:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If for a few minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.51,0:53:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you live where the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.51,0:53:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world lives all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.51,0:53:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you think it's a bad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.51,0:53:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They just think it's a normal day.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.51,0:53:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You get up depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.51,0:53:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you hate everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.51,0:53:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.51,0:53:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with greed and obsession
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.51,0:53:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with retaliation
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.51,0:53:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting even with people,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.51,0:53:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and you think that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.51,0:53:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they live all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.86,0:53:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get a negative thought
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.86,0:53:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.86,0:53:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you ask God to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.86,0:53:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, please help me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.86,0:53:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to get over this angry thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.86,0:53:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and replace it by a pleasant thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.93,0:53:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.72,0:53:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we don't need to go into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.23,0:53:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go and move on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.97,0:53:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I have that one marked?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.97,0:53:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.97,0:53:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated the levels
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.97,0:53:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of many of the world's
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.97,0:54:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,most famous spiritual teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.97,0:54:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a hundred or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.38,0:54:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,People are always writing me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.38,0:54:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,from someplace in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.06,0:54:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I tell them,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.06,0:54:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,look, we calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.06,0:54:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a hundred bona fide teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.06,0:54:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you can't find
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.06,0:54:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your guru on that hundred,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.06,0:54:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.09,0:54:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though there's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.09,0:54:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a hundred well-respected
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.09,0:54:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and verified teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.09,0:54:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they always find, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.09,0:54:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rama Bumchipupu,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.09,0:54:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,who says I should give him
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.60,0:54:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all my money
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.60,0:54:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and go to bed with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.60,0:54:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.56,0:54:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.56,0:54:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, that's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.58,0:54:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.90,0:54:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.25,0:54:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.50,0:54:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just doing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.50,0:54:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the ones I circled?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.50,0:55:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.56,0:55:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.56,0:55:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.33,0:55:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there many more circled?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.13,0:55:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A few.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.83,0:55:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll go through
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.83,0:55:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the next ones real quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.83,0:55:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and we won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.83,0:55:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and play with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.83,0:55:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.12,0:55:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,just move real fast
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.12,0:55:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.12,0:55:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See the great places,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.12,0:55:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual places in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.82,0:55:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one, Golden Rule
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.82,0:55:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates for 405.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.82,0:55:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gregorian Chants, 595.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.82,0:55:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.82,0:55:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Obligations of spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.82,0:55:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Declaration of responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.82,0:55:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.46,0:55:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can calibrate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.46,0:55:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.46,0:55:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.46,0:55:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,here's the crux
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.46,0:55:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of today's lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.46,0:55:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Veneration,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.46,0:55:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.46,0:55:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.46,0:55:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception and essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.46,0:55:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what the world sees
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.46,0:55:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and what it thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.37,0:55:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.37,0:55:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is what
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.37,0:55:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.62,0:55:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.62,0:55:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the next lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.82,0:55:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.82,0:55:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.82,0:55:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.82,0:55:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.82,0:55:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.82,0:56:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.82,0:56:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.82,0:56:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.82,0:56:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.82,0:56:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.10,0:56:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.10,0:56:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.10,0:56:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.10,0:56:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.10,0:56:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.10,0:56:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.10,0:56:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.33,0:56:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.33,0:56:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.33,0:56:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.33,0:56:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.62,0:56:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.62,0:56:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.62,0:56:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.78,0:56:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.78,0:56:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.78,0:56:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.78,0:56:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.78,0:56:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.78,0:56:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.78,0:56:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.78,0:56:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.78,0:56:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.78,0:56:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.78,0:56:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.97,0:56:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.97,0:56:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.97,0:56:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,certain truth from falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.13,0:56:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,out of this, tell the sheep
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.09,0:56:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and wolf in the sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.74,0:56:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.24,0:56:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay. Are we done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.30,0:56:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't. We'll move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.03,0:56:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I circled
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.47,0:56:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,all those. Move on to the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.22,0:56:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,next one. Move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.76,0:57:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.09,0:57:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.92,0:57:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.80,0:57:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.97,0:57:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Reminds me of the Wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.09,0:57:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of Oz. Do not look
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.43,0:57:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,behind this screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.43,0:57:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to keep an eye on the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.72,0:57:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have about
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.34,0:57:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes or so to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.38,0:57:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, alright. Freedom, morality
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.76,0:57:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and ethics. That's not today's
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.42,0:57:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,lecture. Here's what we're
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.40,0:57:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.35,0:57:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the slides on
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.45,0:57:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.42,0:58:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.14,0:58:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,going to be talking about what is
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.04,0:58:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the world? What is the purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.33,0:58:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.29,0:58:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We discovered it's
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.06,0:58:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,God's karmic bailout
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.42,0:58:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,plan. I don't know. I can't
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.15,0:58:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,get the slides right today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.97,0:58:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We need
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.11,0:58:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the world. We're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.07,0:58:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.33,0:59:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.92,0:59:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,157. So we're missing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.40,0:59:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the first three.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.92,0:59:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the world? Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.54,0:59:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, we're ahead of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.53,0:59:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. So there's no
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.04,0:59:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,point of cursing your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.28,0:59:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God, why was I
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.00,0:59:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,born?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.19,0:59:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Being born a human is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.71,0:59:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunate. The consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.07,0:59:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of good karma. If we calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.47,0:59:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that, that comes out at
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.73,0:59:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,455. Now that's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.73,0:59:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what the Buddha teaches pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.20,0:59:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.76,0:59:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the one hand, it's a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.70,0:59:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,good thing to be born a human because
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.32,1:00:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,there are karmic improvements
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.52,1:00:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.40,1:00:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the Buddha warns us
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.52,1:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,to avoid being reborn as
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.58,1:00:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a human.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.92,1:00:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Old age
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.60,1:00:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering and death.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.68,1:00:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.36,1:00:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,avoid it if you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.82,1:00:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you are here, then
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.68,1:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,be glad
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.56,1:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and fortunate
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.80,1:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are here because of good karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.10,1:00:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.22,1:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,here you can overcome
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.88,1:00:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,negative karma and gain positive
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.44,1:00:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,karma. So to me
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.38,1:00:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the world is a world of maximum
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.52,1:00:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.60,1:00:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you can gain good
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.63,1:00:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,karma and undo negative
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.75,1:00:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,karma. Being born
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.17,1:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a human is fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.23,1:00:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And the consequence of good karma
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.97,1:00:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 455.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.05,1:00:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we'll take a negative
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.69,1:00:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,view. The world is a trap of illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.10,1:00:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.72,1:00:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,salvation depends on non-attachment
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.06,1:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to its linear and emotional
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.84,1:01:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,qualities. That only
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.76,1:01:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 230.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.60,1:01:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That only calibrates at 230.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.82,1:01:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The perceived world
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.73,1:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is the result of the projection
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.53,1:01:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.81,1:01:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore akin to a Rorschach
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.71,1:01:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,card, 450.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.85,1:01:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As a psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.01,1:01:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that always appealed to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.81,1:01:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you project
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.69,1:01:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,out onto the world what
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.59,1:01:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you think it is
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.33,1:01:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,because of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.37,1:01:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because of what the world
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.83,1:01:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is. However, you can
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.91,1:01:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,make gross miscalculations
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.93,1:01:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, here kitty, kitty,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.07,1:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,kitty to the tiger.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.99,1:01:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Or play
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.87,1:01:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with the chimpanzee.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.06,1:01:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or tame
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.12,1:01:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a white tiger.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.94,1:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.86,1:01:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,miscalculating with wild animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.34,1:01:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the wild animal
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.74,1:01:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't respond
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.66,1:02:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as a person. So I'll explain
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.86,1:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to you the wild animal phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.34,1:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens with white tigers,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.32,1:02:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,trained lions,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.68,1:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the lady and the lion. In the end
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.88,1:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the lion kills the lady, or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.39,1:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,These trained animals, they suddenly go
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.39,1:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,berserk and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.10,1:02:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And why you cannot trust them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.34,1:02:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.42,1:02:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,animals have a group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.52,1:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Animals have
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.54,1:02:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a perceived
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.14,1:02:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.95,1:02:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They have an individual
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.75,1:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,memory. But their
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.22,1:02:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness is a group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.12,1:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I first learned this
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.24,1:02:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was watching a flock of birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.84,1:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.16,1:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the birds are
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.90,1:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,following each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.06,1:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All thousands of birds are
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.88,1:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,following each other. The sky is black with birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.94,1:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.68,1:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,how can they stay in formation like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.20,1:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Each bird stays in formation
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.88,1:03:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,like a bunch of flying tigers.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.44,1:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a bunch of
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.24,1:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,airplanes, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.88,1:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.73,1:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I suddenly
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.81,1:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,got what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.25,1:03:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Each bird in that flock
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.03,1:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is not following the other birds.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.23,1:03:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.60,1:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.90,1:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, each bird is not
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.00,1:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,following the other birds
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.90,1:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,at all. The assumption
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.18,1:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the bird is following the flock
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.48,1:03:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,due to a density and how
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.18,1:03:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,close they are to the other birds, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.42,1:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening is that there
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.40,1:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is a pattern
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.84,1:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,in their mind, and each
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.14,1:03:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,bird is following not the other
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.10,1:03:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,bird at all, but
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.11,1:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,an energy pattern in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.15,1:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.30,1:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Each bird now is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.82,1:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like a radio turn to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.86,1:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the same radio frequency.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.87,1:04:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So each bird
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.15,1:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is following an inner pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.26,1:04:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.72,1:04:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Each bird
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.44,1:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is following an inner imprint,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.72,1:04:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,an inner pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.01,1:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Each bird is therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.67,1:04:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,individual and yet
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.43,1:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,follows a group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.88,1:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So all animals
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.12,1:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,follow a group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.28,1:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.90,1:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,an ape that seems tame,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.54,1:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,now, his memory
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.64,1:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,track is that this is a safe
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.58,1:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,place to be,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.59,1:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but his group consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.75,1:04:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is that of the animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.61,1:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And at any moment, the white tiger
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.09,1:04:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,will tear your
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.81,1:04:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,carotid artery right out
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.61,1:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's responding
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.92,1:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to the group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.34,1:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, any wild animal
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.96,1:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be trusted
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.58,1:04:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at the level of absolute trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.18,1:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.42,1:05:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,before his
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.70,1:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,group consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.78,1:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,will take over.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.20,1:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And the lion eats the lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.34,1:05:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The white tiger rips out the neck
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.56,1:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,of the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.29,1:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The chimp tears at the lady's face.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.66,1:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.92,1:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the animal is only
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.26,1:05:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,very partially
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.22,1:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.98,1:05:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is more 95%
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.44,1:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the instinctual animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.58,1:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.56,1:05:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you can never safely turn your back
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.82,1:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,on a wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.94,1:05:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you get away
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.30,1:05:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with it many times
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.28,1:05:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean it's safe to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.86,1:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just thought I'd tell you,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.46,1:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,they respond to a group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.66,1:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Below level 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.02,1:05:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,people respond to a group consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.34,1:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Below 200, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.21,1:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the people living
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.67,1:05:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in a violent community,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.83,1:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.11,1:06:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,before they become violent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.70,1:06:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.70,1:06:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,before they begin doing dog
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.28,1:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting and various things like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The group consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.96,1:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to dominate then.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.56,1:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So all of us are
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.24,1:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,under the influence of a group
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.20,1:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,cultural consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.56,1:06:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,plus an individual consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.15,1:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you become
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.19,1:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually evolved,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.61,1:06:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your consciousness becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.07,1:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,progressively more immune
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.75,1:06:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to negativity.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.62,1:06:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And people say, let's go in town
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.84,1:06:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and shoot them all up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.38,1:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, I don't feel like it today.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.04,1:06:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't appeal to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.79,1:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of being a goody-goody.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.59,1:06:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that it has no longer
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.27,1:06:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,any kind of reality to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.63,1:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no kind of reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.36,1:06:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The perceived world is a result
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.12,1:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of a projection of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.14,1:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore like a Rorschach card.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.53,1:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you project out onto the world
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.67,1:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,your view of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.98,1:07:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And depending on what your level of consciousness is,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.98,1:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you can project out onto the world your view of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.00,1:07:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And depending on what your level of consciousness is,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.26,1:07:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I always give the example
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.02,1:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of going to New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.26,1:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I love New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.32,1:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,People will come back from New York City
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.98,1:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, you know, they're all cold
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.08,1:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and unfriendly there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.36,1:07:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Another person will come back
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.28,1:07:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and say, everybody was friendly there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.13,1:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I notice when I go to New York City,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.75,1:07:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you can stop anybody on the street
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.27,1:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and start a conversation
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.35,1:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,just like you knew them forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.95,1:07:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, what do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.35,1:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going up there and the guy will say,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.05,1:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,hell, I think they're spending a lot of taxpayer money on that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.27,1:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right in the middle of a conversation
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.39,1:07:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like you knew you for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.53,1:07:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,People are very, very friendly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.64,1:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're friendly and benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.77,1:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're below 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.75,1:07:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,they say, listen, I don't know you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.47,1:07:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll walk away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.35,1:07:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you see then
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.77,1:07:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is not what you think is out there
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.89,1:08:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but a projection of your own self.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.12,1:08:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we're going to stop here
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.66,1:08:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and take a break for how long?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.22,1:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.96,1:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to review
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.75,1:08:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for those that are new,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.85,1:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because quite a few knew,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.73,1:08:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,all that we've summarized
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.27,1:08:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so far,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.76,1:08:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and that'll bring us up to date
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.36,1:08:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for today's lecture.
